data.description: One owner home!  This home was built by the current owner with many well thought out upgrades in place.  It has been lovingly maintained and updated.  What a gem!  With windows all along the entire side of the home facing the park, this home has amazingly peaceful views of the gazebo, ponds and fountains.  You won't be disappointed in this home!  It is spacious, light and a very open floor plan.  There is an extended screened lanai on the back of the home overlooking not just one, but two ponds with lit fountains. The kitchen features a center island with seating for two, Corian countertops and new dropped lighting.  The  master suite offers a tray ceiling and stunning views of the lake and fountain.  Most of the home has new screen blinds to reduce heat and light
